name: Antbull Exquisite Relics #3 - Flare
description:
Antbulls appear in gloomy ambients. Memories of caves are shared to those to embarked 3D worlds where and when things were simpler. What makes them more complex? More vertices? More polygons? Or the uncanny never ending repetitions of History?
